  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "里見八犬伝。滝沢馬琴の名作小説をRPGにアレンジした作品。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Hakkenden, and variations, may refer to:\n\nNansō Satomi Hakkenden, an epic 19th century serial novel by Kyokutei Bakin\nOr adaptations of the story, including:\n\nSatomi Hakkenden (1983), known as Legend of the Eight Samurai, a martial arts fantasy film\nThe Hakkenden (1990–1995), an anime OVA series by Anime International Company\nIdol Hakkenden (1989), a Japanese text adventure video game\nShin Hakkenden (1999), a Japanese anime series\nHakkenden: Eight Dogs of the East (Hakkenden: Tōhō Hakken Ibun), a 2005 manga and 2013 Japanese anime series adaptation",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    }
  ],
